Question about multiple dispatch, i have this MVE:
```
using MathOptInterface
const MOI = MathOptInterface
function ts(
           ::Type{F},
           ::Type{S}
       ) where {S &lt;: Union{
           MOI.LessThan{Float64},
           MOI.GreaterThan{Float64},
           MOI.EqualTo{Float64}
       }} where {F &lt;: Union{
           MOI.SingleVariable,
           MOI.ScalarAffineFunction{Float64},
           MOI.ScalarQuadraticFunction{Float64}
       }}
           return true
       end
```
However:
```
ts(MOI.LessThan{Float64},MOI.ScalarAffineFunction{Float64})
ERROR: MethodError: no method matching ts(::Type{MathOptInterface.LessThan{Float64}}, ::Type{MathOptInterface.ScalarAffineFunction{Float64}})
```
Why does it fail, i would expect it to return true?
